Prerequisites

2) This class assumes you have a basic working knowledge of R (e.g. familiarity with matrices, vectors, lists, and data frames)

Prerequisites

 

1) This class assumes you have both R and RStudio installed;

2) This class assumes you have a basic working knowledge of R (e.g. familiarity with matrices, vectors, lists, and data frames)

3) This class assumes you have basic data processing skills in R (e.g. cleaning, merging, or reshaping data in R); and,

4) This class assumes you have beginner-level programming knowledge (e.g. functions and loops).

5) It may be easier to follow along with the class via the Google Chrome Browser than others.
